WEBVTT

01:53.360 --> 01:55.320
I'm coming.

01:58.160 --> 01:59.000
Jingu.

01:59.080 --> 01:59.720
Auntie.

02:00.840 --> 02:01.900
You are back again.

02:02.880 --> 02:04.920
Auntie, I lost my house key.

02:05.200 --> 02:06.360
I don't know if I forgot it

02:06.360 --> 02:07.960
or left it in Qingyun's room.

02:08.680 --> 02:09.840
Then come in, come in.

02:09.840 --> 02:11.400
Let's look for it together. Come.

02:11.400 --> 02:12.000
Okay.

02:34.400 --> 02:36.930
Could your key have fallen into my underwear?

02:41.400 --> 02:42.160
I mean,

02:42.560 --> 02:44.280
did you even bring it at all?

02:46.040 --> 02:47.240
It's too late today.

02:48.480 --> 02:49.720
Why don't you go back first,

02:49.720 --> 02:51.200
and I'll keep looking for it.

02:51.200 --> 02:54.260
If I find it, I'll have Qingyun bring it to you tomorrow.

02:54.480 --> 02:56.210
But my parents went to Beijing.

02:57.160 --> 02:58.760
If I can't find the house key,

02:59.160 --> 03:00.760
I might not be able to go home.

03:01.600 --> 03:02.640
It's no big deal.

03:02.840 --> 03:05.160
Since you guys have to tutor together these next few days anyway,

03:05.160 --> 03:07.440
and it's a hassle to go back and forth every day,

03:07.440 --> 03:08.560
why don't you just stay here?

03:08.560 --> 03:10.560
Make yourself at home. Don't be shy.

03:10.560 --> 03:11.760
No, it's fine, Auntie. I...

03:11.760 --> 03:12.840
What do you mean 'no need'?

03:12.840 --> 03:14.240
It's so late and you don't have your keys.

03:14.240 --> 03:15.370
Where are you going?

03:15.440 --> 03:16.440
Just listen to me.

03:17.120 --> 03:17.800
But Mom,

03:18.280 --> 03:20.400
our place is so small. Where will he sleep?

03:20.400 --> 03:21.200
This child.

03:21.600 --> 03:23.079
Why are you being so unreasonable?

03:23.079 --> 03:25.680
Jingu came all the way here to tutor you.

03:25.840 --> 03:27.640
And we haven't even paid him yet.

03:31.240 --> 03:34.640
This sofa is made of wood, it's really impossible to sleep on.

03:34.680 --> 03:35.840
I won't trouble you, Auntie.

03:35.840 --> 03:37.800
I can stay in a hotel. I have money.

03:38.040 --> 03:39.440
Why spend that money?

03:39.480 --> 03:41.680
It's not like we don't have enough room.

03:41.800 --> 03:42.640
Mom.

03:44.480 --> 03:44.960
You...

03:45.160 --> 03:46.400
Qingyun's bed is big.

03:46.440 --> 03:47.370
How about you two

03:47.640 --> 03:49.160
sleep here? It's big enough.

03:49.160 --> 03:49.960
You are both grown-ups.

03:49.960 --> 03:51.440
It shouldn't be inconvenient.

03:51.440 --> 03:52.500
It's settled then.

03:52.680 --> 03:53.720
No, no.

03:54.040 --> 03:54.600
Mom.

03:55.240 --> 03:56.100
Don't 'Mom' me.

03:56.760 --> 03:58.560
If not, you can sleep on the sofa.

04:00.920 --> 04:02.840
Jingu, in the bathroom...

04:02.880 --> 04:04.410
We have all the toiletries.

04:05.640 --> 04:07.320
I'll go find you a set of pajamas.

04:07.320 --> 04:08.000
They're Qingyun's.

04:08.000 --> 04:09.200
You two are about the same height,

04:09.200 --> 04:10.160
they'll definitely fit.

04:10.160 --> 04:11.000
They're brand new.

04:11.000 --> 04:12.280
Ma'am, I...

04:18.200 --> 04:18.800
Then,

04:19.800 --> 04:21.079
sorry to trouble you.

04:27.000 --> 04:29.060
You have to at least give me a blanket.

04:29.720 --> 04:31.450
Let me make this clear upfront.

04:31.840 --> 04:34.040
If you dare to fart, snore,

04:34.120 --> 04:35.280
or cross this line,

04:36.360 --> 04:37.760
I'll kick you off the bed.

04:38.120 --> 04:40.120
That's what I wanted to tell you too.

05:26.480 --> 05:27.160
Mom,

05:27.680 --> 05:28.600
is the food ready?

05:28.600 --> 05:29.860
I'm starving to death.

06:03.600 --> 06:05.130
What... What are you doing?

06:06.280 --> 06:08.810
What are you eating this early in the morning?

06:14.080 --> 06:14.960
Good morning, Auntie.

06:14.960 --> 06:15.680
Morning, Grandpa. Morning, Yuanbao.

06:15.680 --> 06:16.840
Yuanbao, come on, sit.

06:16.840 --> 06:17.520
Time to eat, Bao.

06:17.520 --> 06:18.280
Let's eat.

06:21.920 --> 06:23.160
You two...

06:23.920 --> 06:24.320
Guo...

06:26.200 --> 06:29.000
You... didn't you go home yesterday?

06:29.920 --> 06:31.250
I couldn't find my keys.

06:31.400 --> 06:32.930
My parents went to Beijing.

06:34.560 --> 06:37.480
So you two shared a bed all night?

06:46.800 --> 06:48.320
Come, sit.

06:49.159 --> 06:51.360
They slept in Qingyun's bed yesterday.

06:52.200 --> 06:53.760
Eat up. Don't dawdle.

07:01.720 --> 07:03.040
Jingu is here too.

07:03.080 --> 07:04.280
That's great.

07:04.360 --> 07:05.760
Come, let's eat.

07:07.080 --> 07:08.200
Morning, Grandma.

07:08.760 --> 07:09.440
Morning.

07:09.600 --> 07:10.800
Have some congee.

07:10.880 --> 07:11.480
Sit.

07:11.520 --> 07:12.200
Okay.

07:14.200 --> 07:16.720
Here, one pair for each.

07:17.800 --> 07:18.860
Thank you, Auntie.

07:19.400 --> 07:22.000
Recently, they've been tutoring together.

07:23.200 --> 07:25.400
Jingu's parents went to Beijing again.

07:25.560 --> 07:27.720
Jingu, just stay here.

07:27.840 --> 07:29.100
Make yourself at home.

07:29.800 --> 07:32.130
It'll be easier for you to study together.

07:32.280 --> 07:33.840
The Olympics are coming up.

07:34.040 --> 07:35.720
We can watch them together.

07:35.800 --> 07:37.040
It'll be fun.

07:37.480 --> 07:39.000
Sorry for the trouble, Auntie.

07:39.000 --> 07:40.480
Will I be bothering you?

07:42.080 --> 07:43.320
I actually think so.

07:43.640 --> 07:45.560
You dawdle like a girl.

07:46.280 --> 07:48.440
Your classmate is tutoring you and can't go home.

07:48.440 --> 07:50.040
Shouldn't he stay here?

07:50.280 --> 07:52.000
You have no manners.

07:52.800 --> 07:55.200
Auntie, I'd better stay in a hotel.

07:55.360 --> 07:56.040
No.

07:56.360 --> 07:57.920
Listen to me and stay here.

07:58.320 --> 08:00.160
A hotel isn't as comfortable as home.

08:00.160 --> 08:01.120
Exactly.

08:01.280 --> 08:04.040
You can study and progress together.

08:04.440 --> 08:06.920
It's like a happy family.

08:07.120 --> 08:09.040
Grandma will cook for you every day.

08:09.040 --> 08:09.680
Exactly.

08:10.000 --> 08:11.040
Seeing you guys,

08:11.240 --> 08:13.300
makes me feel like I'm seeing Xiaoyu.

08:13.520 --> 08:14.240
You guys

08:14.760 --> 08:16.320
are all his classmates.

08:16.640 --> 08:18.920
This kind of friendship is so precious.

08:19.400 --> 08:20.960
Here, Jingu, eat more.

08:21.040 --> 08:22.120
Here, Jingu.

08:22.680 --> 08:23.720
Have some dough sticks.

08:23.720 --> 08:24.850
Thank you, Grandpa.

08:26.360 --> 08:27.240
Alright then.

08:28.840 --> 08:29.880
Here, have an egg.

08:30.200 --> 08:30.680
Thank you, Auntie.

08:30.680 --> 08:31.760
You're welcome.

08:39.960 --> 08:41.240
Grandma, here,

08:41.520 --> 08:42.400
try this.

08:43.919 --> 08:45.600
Jingu, you're so sweet.

08:47.520 --> 08:48.580
Grandma, eat this.

08:48.600 --> 08:49.480
This is good.

08:49.840 --> 08:51.900
Qingyun, you've grown sensible too.

08:52.440 --> 08:53.840
Here, eat this, Grandma.

08:54.000 --> 08:55.060
This is delicious.

08:55.080 --> 08:56.080
Jingu,

08:56.160 --> 08:58.320
how are you so good at studying?

09:00.920 --> 09:02.520
This one is tastier. Have some.

09:02.520 --> 09:03.850
Here, have some greens.

09:04.200 --> 09:05.480
Grandma.

09:05.960 --> 09:07.000
Grandma. Grandma.

09:07.000 --> 09:07.720
Grandma.

09:08.520 --> 09:09.160
Grandma.

09:28.600 --> 09:31.320
Global cooling.

09:32.120 --> 09:33.560
Which one of you two young men

09:33.560 --> 09:35.840
can help Grandma change a lightbulb?

09:36.400 --> 09:37.600
Grandma, I'll do it.

09:38.800 --> 09:40.400
Jingu, you can do anything.

09:40.960 --> 09:41.600
Let's go, Grandma.

09:41.600 --> 09:42.920
When our Yuanbao grows up,

09:42.920 --> 09:45.600
she needs to find someone who can do anything.

09:48.200 --> 09:49.400
Grandma, I'll do it.

09:55.040 --> 09:57.080
Why is this tile cracked?

10:04.920 --> 10:06.640
Why is this table broken?

10:16.240 --> 10:18.560
When did this glass break?

10:26.480 --> 10:28.320
Why is this wall dirty?

10:45.480 --> 10:46.800
Is this my house?

10:47.280 --> 10:48.560
It's so clean.

10:53.280 --> 10:54.340
You are so capable.

10:54.960 --> 10:55.080
Let's form a contracting team.

10:55.080 --> 10:56.200
Let's form a contracting team.

10:56.200 --> 10:58.260
We'll definitely make a lot of money.

11:01.760 --> 11:02.480
Ten.

11:07.760 --> 11:08.440
Five.

11:15.480 --> 11:17.240
I love you, China.

11:17.440 --> 11:18.560
I love you, China.

11:18.600 --> 11:19.440
Go China!

11:22.600 --> 11:28.560
I love you, China.

11:29.280 --> 11:35.520
I love you, China.

11:35.840 --> 11:42.320
I will dedicate my most beautiful youth to you,

11:42.320 --> 11:45.720
my mother,

11:45.920 --> 11:51.040
my motherland.

12:22.600 --> 12:24.000
So beautiful.

12:27.080 --> 12:29.560
When we go to college in Beijing,

12:29.840 --> 12:32.160
I'll take you to see the Bird's Nest, okay?

12:32.160 --> 12:33.360
With your grades,

12:33.440 --> 12:35.170
you still want to go to Beijing?

12:35.840 --> 12:38.240
Just wait and see. I will definitely get in.

12:38.440 --> 12:40.440
Okay, then it's a deal.

12:41.880 --> 12:42.760
It's a deal.

14:42.400 --> 14:43.920
Go China!

14:44.000 --> 14:45.680
Go seniors!

14:55.960 --> 14:58.400
Senior year, here we come.

15:06.280 --> 15:07.920
Welcome back, class.

15:08.440 --> 15:09.560
Starting today,

15:09.760 --> 15:11.820
we officially enter our senior year.

15:11.960 --> 15:13.040
Which means

15:13.200 --> 15:15.280
we need to start preparing for the Gaokao.

15:15.280 --> 15:16.760
Senior year is not like your first two years.

15:16.760 --> 15:18.240
After we finish the new lessons...

15:18.240 --> 15:20.160
We will have four rounds of general review,

15:20.160 --> 15:21.840
so I hope you can all

15:21.880 --> 15:23.000
keep up with me.

15:23.120 --> 15:23.760
I don't want

15:23.760 --> 15:25.160
any of you to fall behind.

15:25.360 --> 15:26.290
For senior year,

15:26.320 --> 15:28.320
besides an extra hour of evening study,

15:28.320 --> 15:29.120
each weekend,

15:29.160 --> 15:31.420
you'll only have Sunday afternoons off.

15:31.440 --> 15:32.170
So that means

15:32.200 --> 15:33.840
we have no rest time at all.

15:33.920 --> 15:34.520
Yeah.

15:34.560 --> 15:37.440
Then P.E. classes are completely out of the question.

15:37.440 --> 15:39.100
All right, stop complaining.

15:39.240 --> 15:40.520
During your senior year,

15:40.520 --> 15:42.480
aside from eating, sleeping, and using the bathroom,

15:42.480 --> 15:44.880
you must all swim in the ocean of knowledge.

15:45.000 --> 15:46.280
As for those who are good swimmers,

15:46.280 --> 15:47.160
don't be arrogant.

15:47.160 --> 15:49.120
Because haven't you heard?

15:49.240 --> 15:51.000
Good swimmers are the ones who drown.

15:51.000 --> 15:53.000
Carelessness will cost you dearly.

15:53.040 --> 15:55.300
As for those who can only doggy paddle...

15:55.320 --> 15:56.400
Don't lose heart.

15:56.480 --> 15:57.920
Maybe as you keep paddling,

15:57.920 --> 15:59.560
you'll become a champion swimmer.

15:59.560 --> 16:01.160
Anyway, in this senior year,

16:01.640 --> 16:04.080
you must swim to the shores of your dreams.

16:04.280 --> 16:04.880
Keep it up!

16:05.160 --> 16:06.000
Keep it up!

16:06.400 --> 16:07.730
Also, an announcement.

16:08.120 --> 16:10.000
The annual National Physics Competition

16:10.000 --> 16:11.160
is about to begin.

16:11.560 --> 16:12.840
You all know this competition is

16:12.840 --> 16:13.720
very fierce.

16:13.840 --> 16:16.240
Not only middle and high school students,

16:16.280 --> 16:17.400
but also college students.

16:17.400 --> 16:18.640
However, this is currently the

16:18.640 --> 16:20.600
most prestigious national physics competition.

16:20.600 --> 16:21.880
Moreover, the competition results

16:21.880 --> 16:23.560
are internationally recognized.

16:23.560 --> 16:25.360
I heard the prize money this time

16:25.520 --> 16:27.400
is around 100,000 yuan.

16:27.600 --> 16:28.840
100,000.

16:30.120 --> 16:32.880
Each school only has one spot.

16:33.440 --> 16:35.080
Based on our class's past performance,

16:35.080 --> 16:37.400
I recommend Meng Jingu.

16:37.720 --> 16:38.960
Does anyone have any objections?

16:38.960 --> 16:40.440
No, no, no.

16:40.840 --> 16:43.440
Meng Jingu, you have no problem with it, right?

16:45.840 --> 16:47.440
When I announced it just now,

16:47.480 --> 16:48.680
you looked worried.

16:49.160 --> 16:50.560
Do you have any concerns?

16:51.920 --> 16:54.240
I think someone else is more suitable than me.

16:54.240 --> 16:54.960
Who?

16:55.400 --> 16:56.200
Mu Qingjun.

16:57.560 --> 16:58.720
Mu... Mu Qingjun.

17:00.680 --> 17:02.120
These are the physics problems we made for each other

17:02.120 --> 17:04.400
when we were pen pals before we met.

17:04.480 --> 17:05.240
Take a look.

17:05.359 --> 17:06.720
When I first transferred here,

17:06.720 --> 17:08.180
in our first monthly exam,

17:08.280 --> 17:09.680
there was a difficult physics question.

17:09.680 --> 17:10.609
Do you remember?

17:10.720 --> 17:11.650
Yes, I remember.

17:12.240 --> 17:14.440
I remember I was sitting behind him.

17:15.200 --> 17:17.359
I saw he finished that question first.

17:17.480 --> 17:18.760
So he didn't copy mine.

17:19.640 --> 17:21.880
But he admitted he cheated,

17:22.040 --> 17:23.440
so I didn't say anything.

17:24.480 --> 17:25.880
That's impossible.

17:27.119 --> 17:28.720
Why would he admit he cheated

17:29.440 --> 17:31.080
and always finish at the bottom?

17:31.080 --> 17:32.800
Actually, he is a genius.

17:33.360 --> 17:35.520
So I don't want his talent to be buried.

17:36.000 --> 17:37.080
If you don't believe me, sir,

17:37.080 --> 17:39.880
you can compare it with his previous handwriting.

17:49.840 --> 17:51.900
As to why, I'm not really sure either.

17:52.240 --> 17:53.240
But I promised him

17:53.320 --> 17:54.650
I would keep his secret.

17:56.800 --> 17:58.640
Okay, I understand.

17:58.880 --> 18:00.480
I won't mention this to him.

18:01.760 --> 18:04.160
You go back first. I'll think of something.

18:15.280 --> 18:16.040
Yuanbao.

18:16.520 --> 18:18.080
Auntie, why are you here?

18:18.200 --> 18:19.640
I cut some fruit for you.

18:19.760 --> 18:20.520
Here, try it.

18:24.440 --> 18:25.100
Is it sweet?

18:25.160 --> 18:26.490
Yes. Thank you, Auntie.

18:26.720 --> 18:28.840
Where are Grandpa and Grandma? Did they go out?

18:28.840 --> 18:30.300
They went square dancing.

18:33.320 --> 18:35.180
Ever since Grandpa Gong moved in,

18:35.280 --> 18:37.480
Grandma's mental state has been much better.

18:37.480 --> 18:39.740
The two of them can look after each other.

18:39.960 --> 18:42.040
When you go to college in the future,

18:42.200 --> 18:43.840
we won't be so worried.

18:44.920 --> 18:46.280
They were talking and laughing,

18:46.280 --> 18:47.680
and I was quite happy too.

18:50.560 --> 18:51.320
Yuanbao.

18:52.560 --> 18:55.360
Your uncle is pulling strings in the UK now,

18:55.640 --> 18:58.970
trying to apply for study abroad quotas for you and Qingyun.

18:59.040 --> 18:59.840
I heard

18:59.920 --> 19:01.760
it's a very good university.

19:02.360 --> 19:03.800
With the current study abroad fever,

19:03.800 --> 19:05.280
many people who come back from abroad

19:05.280 --> 19:07.160
can find very good jobs.

19:08.040 --> 19:10.680
Your uncle and I have to plan for you.

19:11.280 --> 19:12.280
Don't you think?

19:13.280 --> 19:16.600
Auntie, if we study abroad,

19:17.320 --> 19:19.450
will Grandpa and Grandma go together?

19:23.720 --> 19:25.780
Grandpa and Grandma are getting old.

19:26.560 --> 19:28.820
If they suddenly go to a new environment,

19:29.040 --> 19:30.840
they might not adapt to it.

19:31.320 --> 19:34.360
So we can't take Grandpa and Grandma with us.

19:34.600 --> 19:36.000
Your uncle and I

19:36.080 --> 19:37.810
are also struggling with this.

19:38.400 --> 19:40.930
After all, we are not familiar with the place.

19:41.160 --> 19:43.290
Your uncle's job has just stabilized.

19:43.440 --> 19:45.520
Taking care of such a big family

19:46.800 --> 19:48.520
is indeed very stressful.

19:49.760 --> 19:50.600
Auntie.

19:51.640 --> 19:53.640
I only have Grandma.

19:54.560 --> 19:56.120
If I go abroad,

19:56.680 --> 19:58.610
and something happens to Grandma,

19:58.640 --> 20:00.900
I wouldn't be able to come back in a hurry.

20:02.240 --> 20:03.560
Don't worry.

20:03.920 --> 20:05.580
This hasn't been decided yet.

20:06.320 --> 20:08.640
Auntie is just

20:08.720 --> 20:10.720
analyzing it objectively with you.

20:11.040 --> 20:12.520
If we really go abroad,

20:12.800 --> 20:14.800
we are not going there to enjoy life.

20:14.840 --> 20:16.770
You and Qingyun will have classes,

20:17.200 --> 20:18.880
and your uncle and I will have to work.

20:18.880 --> 20:21.000
Leaving Grandpa and Grandma at home alone,

20:21.000 --> 20:22.530
surrounded by foreigners,

20:22.880 --> 20:24.400
and they don't speak the language.

20:24.400 --> 20:27.120
If they want to go out to buy groceries or take a walk,

20:27.120 --> 20:28.380
it would be difficult.

20:29.040 --> 20:30.720
Arriving in a new environment,

20:30.720 --> 20:32.120
leaving their hometown,

20:32.280 --> 20:35.080
is really not a good thing for the elderly.

20:39.160 --> 20:39.960
Auntie.

20:41.000 --> 20:42.200
Then I won't go.

20:48.040 --> 20:49.360
Okay.

20:49.760 --> 20:51.720
This hasn't been finalized yet.

20:51.800 --> 20:54.130
Your uncle just went to pull some strings.

20:54.480 --> 20:56.040
It might not even work out.

20:56.640 --> 20:57.840
Don't be nervous.

20:58.480 --> 21:00.280
Auntie promises you

21:01.480 --> 21:03.880
that I will arrange everything properly.

21:04.040 --> 21:04.840
Okay?

21:06.520 --> 21:07.980
It's late. Go to bed early.

21:08.400 --> 21:10.600
Eat those fruits before you go to sleep.

21:10.920 --> 21:11.920
Don't waste them.

21:12.440 --> 21:13.500
Auntie is leaving.

21:19.280 --> 21:20.120
Classmates.

21:20.640 --> 21:22.000
Through the school leaders,

21:22.000 --> 21:23.920
After a meeting with all the physics teachers,

21:23.920 --> 21:25.120
the spot to represent our school

21:25.120 --> 21:27.040
in the National Physics Competition

21:27.040 --> 21:28.160
has fallen to our class.

21:28.160 --> 21:29.240
This person is...

21:31.400 --> 21:32.400
Mu Qingjun.

21:33.600 --> 21:34.760
Mu Qingjun?

21:36.480 --> 21:38.040
That's right, Mu Qingjun.

21:39.840 --> 21:40.760
Mr. Tian,

21:41.520 --> 21:43.400
I think you must be mistaken.

21:43.560 --> 21:45.800
Mu Qingjun and I grew up together.

21:46.160 --> 21:48.360
I know his level better than anyone.

21:48.800 --> 21:50.800
His physics homework,

21:50.840 --> 21:53.720
I even helped him with it at home.

21:54.280 --> 21:57.200
If you ask him to participate in the National Physics Competition,

21:57.200 --> 21:58.860
wouldn't that embarrass him?

21:58.920 --> 22:00.160
Exactly, sir.

22:00.320 --> 22:01.920
With Yuanbao's grades,

22:02.080 --> 22:03.800
his tutoring would make him dead last every time.

22:03.800 --> 22:05.080
I don't believe it either.

22:05.080 --> 22:06.120
Let alone you,

22:06.320 --> 22:08.120
at first, I didn't believe it either.

22:08.120 --> 22:09.520
But now it's been proven.

22:09.800 --> 22:11.440
This kid is really impressive.

22:11.440 --> 22:12.520
Not only is he good at physics,

22:12.520 --> 22:14.980
he's even better at acting. He fooled us all.

22:15.040 --> 22:17.160
Yuanbao, he grew up with you.

22:17.360 --> 22:19.120
And you didn't even know his true level.

22:19.120 --> 22:21.160
You tell me, how good is his act?

22:21.920 --> 22:23.880
How is this possible?

22:24.360 --> 22:25.800
Why would he pretend?

22:26.080 --> 22:27.600
There's no reason, sir.

22:28.080 --> 22:29.410
I don't know about that.

22:29.480 --> 22:31.080
But that doesn't matter now.

22:31.080 --> 22:32.160
The important thing is

22:32.160 --> 22:33.400
that he has been listed by the school

22:33.400 --> 22:34.880
as a key student for cultivation.

22:34.880 --> 22:35.800
You should also work hard.

22:35.800 --> 22:36.460
Have a seat.

22:36.480 --> 22:37.680
Really?

22:37.760 --> 22:39.920
He was just pretending to be bad at studying?

22:39.920 --> 22:42.580
Even Yuanbao, who grew up with him, didn't know.

22:42.680 --> 22:43.400
All right.

22:43.800 --> 22:45.360
It's a good thing that Mu Qingjun is good at studying.

22:45.360 --> 22:46.720
When you are with him,

22:46.760 --> 22:48.290
you can also learn from him.

22:49.480 --> 22:51.610
Mu Qingjun, you came at the right time.

22:51.640 --> 22:53.000
I happen to have a few copies

22:53.000 --> 22:55.280
of previous National Physics Competition papers.

22:55.280 --> 22:56.040
Take a look.

22:56.120 --> 22:56.800
No.

22:57.320 --> 22:58.800
Why are you showing me this?

22:58.800 --> 23:00.130
I don't know how to do it.

23:01.160 --> 23:02.220
Still pretending?

23:05.560 --> 23:06.620
Come, look at this.

23:12.120 --> 23:13.180
Look for yourself.

23:15.800 --> 23:16.720
No, this...

23:17.000 --> 23:20.440
This isn't mine. Sir,

23:20.600 --> 23:21.800
you made a mistake.

23:22.440 --> 23:23.720
Mistake? Impossible.

23:23.840 --> 23:25.280
With this spider-like handwriting of yours,

23:25.280 --> 23:27.410
I compared so many before I caught you.

23:29.280 --> 23:30.920
Sir, you know what my level is.

23:30.920 --> 23:32.120
You know that.

23:32.360 --> 23:34.120
How could this be mine?

23:34.200 --> 23:36.000
I didn't know your level before,

23:36.240 --> 23:37.700
but I understand it today.

23:38.240 --> 23:40.920
Sir, what do I have to say for you to believe me?

23:41.280 --> 23:42.760
I don't know anything anyway.

23:42.760 --> 23:45.160
Don't expect me to win glory for the school.

23:45.480 --> 23:46.840
I don't have that ability.

23:46.840 --> 23:47.560
Mu Qingjun.

23:48.280 --> 23:49.880
Don't be in a hurry to refuse.

23:50.320 --> 23:51.400
Now this matter,

23:51.560 --> 23:53.040
has already spread in the school.

23:53.040 --> 23:54.800
They say you are a hidden genius.

23:54.800 --> 23:56.640
Whether you go to this competition or not,

23:56.640 --> 23:58.760
this matter is a done deal.

23:59.360 --> 24:00.400
If you don't go,

24:00.760 --> 24:03.240
many students will definitely think you are very selfish,

24:03.240 --> 24:05.440
unwilling to contribute to the school.

24:05.720 --> 24:06.520
Stop sighing.

24:06.520 --> 24:07.520
You study so well,

24:07.760 --> 24:08.920
and you deceived all the teachers.

24:08.920 --> 24:09.720
Why?

24:09.760 --> 24:12.360
No, how did you get this?

24:14.000 --> 24:15.600
Did Meng Jingu give it to you?

24:16.800 --> 24:17.560
It was me.

24:22.880 --> 24:24.720
What do you mean? Are you crazy?

24:24.840 --> 24:26.040
Don't be angry first.

24:26.920 --> 24:28.560
This time, due to personal reasons,

24:28.560 --> 24:30.680
I can't participate in this competition.

24:30.680 --> 24:32.800
Setting aside winning glory for the school,

24:32.800 --> 24:34.680
this competition is indeed very important

24:34.680 --> 24:36.120
for your future college applications.

24:36.120 --> 24:38.440
Rather than letting a mediocre person waste the opportunity,

24:38.440 --> 24:39.640
it's better if you go.

24:39.880 --> 24:41.640
There's only one chance in high school.

24:41.640 --> 24:42.900
You should cherish it.

24:43.240 --> 24:46.040
Just work hard for your future self.

24:47.040 --> 24:49.100
Do you need to worry about my affairs?

24:49.160 --> 24:50.240
Why didn't you ask me first?

24:50.240 --> 24:51.120
If I asked you, would you go?

24:51.120 --> 24:51.920
Of course not.

24:51.920 --> 24:52.880
Then that's it.

24:55.920 --> 24:56.480
You,

24:56.560 --> 24:57.360
Mu Qingjun.

24:57.440 --> 24:59.560
you really messed me up.

25:00.200 --> 25:01.560
I really don't understand.

25:01.560 --> 25:03.880
Isn't it good to be a good student cared for by teachers?

25:03.880 --> 25:04.600
Mu Qingjun.

25:04.760 --> 25:05.440
Mu Qingjun!

25:05.520 --> 25:07.440
Mu Qingyun is a physics genius.

25:07.920 --> 25:09.640
He kept it from everyone before.

25:09.640 --> 25:11.360
Even the teachers just found out.

25:11.360 --> 25:14.200
They even asked him to join the National Physics Olympiad.

25:14.200 --> 25:15.000
No way.

25:15.600 --> 25:17.280
Others might not know,

25:17.320 --> 25:18.640
but how could Xiong Yuanbao not know?

25:18.640 --> 25:19.920
They are so close.

25:20.280 --> 25:22.040
Mu Qingyun wouldn't hide it from her, right?

25:22.040 --> 25:23.240
Not necessarily.

25:23.360 --> 25:24.600
Judging by her expression,

25:24.600 --> 25:26.200
she doesn't look like she knows.

25:26.200 --> 25:27.240
That shouldn't be.

25:27.240 --> 25:29.680
Mu Qingyun and Xiong Yuanbao

25:29.680 --> 25:30.800
are childhood sweethearts.

25:30.800 --> 25:31.860
For such a big deal,

25:31.920 --> 25:33.400
Mu Qingyun wouldn't keep it from her.

25:33.400 --> 25:35.000
I think it's just Xiong Yuanbao

25:35.000 --> 25:36.520
who keeps pestering Mu Qingyun.

25:36.520 --> 25:38.080
When Mu Qingyun was bad at studying,

25:38.080 --> 25:40.280
they didn't look out of place together.

25:40.320 --> 25:41.760
But things are different now.

25:41.760 --> 25:44.020
Mu Qingyun is now the top guy at Zhicheng.

25:44.080 --> 25:45.560
He's good-looking and great at studying.

25:45.560 --> 25:47.960
He's literally the male lead out of a novel.

25:48.000 --> 25:49.440
They look so awkward

25:49.960 --> 25:51.160
standing together.

26:02.880 --> 26:03.760
Yuanbao.

26:05.240 --> 26:06.400
Mom promises you,

26:06.560 --> 26:08.040
I will be back soon.

26:13.280 --> 26:15.210
You remember the Diamond Princess

26:15.480 --> 26:17.010
and the Elf's Appointment.

26:17.680 --> 26:20.810
Why don't you remember that I hate being lied to the most?

26:23.920 --> 26:24.560
Yuanbao.

26:26.160 --> 26:27.090
Get out of my way.

26:27.160 --> 26:28.440
Yuanbao, listen to me.

26:28.560 --> 26:30.760
I really didn't mean to hide it from you.

26:31.280 --> 26:32.200
Do you know that

26:33.200 --> 26:35.330
I hate it the most when people lie to me?

26:36.800 --> 26:37.600
I know.

26:37.880 --> 26:39.320
Then do you remember

26:40.000 --> 26:41.160
that you swore

26:42.160 --> 26:44.000
never to lie to me?

26:44.680 --> 26:45.360
I remember.

26:45.840 --> 26:46.770
All these years,

26:47.600 --> 26:49.130
you dragged me to tutor you,

26:50.320 --> 26:52.480
pretending to know nothing.

26:53.000 --> 26:55.320
Watching me rack my brains to teach you

26:55.760 --> 26:57.200
and explain problems to you...

26:57.200 --> 26:58.840
Did you find it amusing?

26:59.080 --> 27:00.000
No.

27:00.280 --> 27:01.880
It's not like that, Yuanbao.

27:01.920 --> 27:03.050
I rejected Mr. Tian.

27:03.480 --> 27:04.520
They got it wrong.

27:04.600 --> 27:07.240
If Mr. Tian hadn't mentioned it in class today,

27:08.080 --> 27:10.010
how long were you going to lie to me?

27:11.520 --> 27:14.280
What? Were you planning to amaze everyone

27:14.600 --> 27:15.880
during the college entrance exam

27:15.880 --> 27:18.080
and crush me with your genius scores?

27:19.000 --> 27:19.730
No, Yuanbao.

27:19.800 --> 27:21.530
I really never thought of that.

27:21.960 --> 27:23.690
Watching a poor student like me

27:24.280 --> 27:26.540
rack my brains to teach a genius like you,

27:26.960 --> 27:28.440
playing me for a fool...

27:28.800 --> 27:30.040
Is it fun?

27:33.160 --> 27:34.620
When I argued with Mr. Tian

27:35.440 --> 27:38.370
because I was afraid you'd make a fool of yourself...

27:39.400 --> 27:41.360
It seems I am the biggest joke.

27:43.760 --> 27:45.800
A poor student like me is too stupid

27:46.080 --> 27:48.210
to understand these twists and turns.

27:48.800 --> 27:51.660
How do I deserve to be friends with a genius like you?

27:52.360 --> 27:53.040
Yuanbao.

27:57.080 --> 27:57.920
Are you okay?

28:15.920 --> 28:16.450
Grandma.

28:16.560 --> 28:17.760
Why didn't you wake me up?

28:17.760 --> 28:19.290
I'm almost late for school.

28:19.440 --> 28:20.840
I called you several times.

28:20.840 --> 28:21.800
You slept like a pig

28:21.800 --> 28:23.520
and just refused to get up.

28:26.520 --> 28:28.320
Here, take these two apples.

28:29.240 --> 28:30.720
I don't need the apples.

28:31.160 --> 28:32.880
You haven't eaten any fruit for days.

28:32.880 --> 28:35.360
Take them to school and share them with Qingjun.

28:35.360 --> 28:36.520
Okay, I got it.

28:36.520 --> 28:37.720
Be careful on the way.

28:38.320 --> 28:39.080
I got it.

28:39.120 --> 28:40.280
Come home early after school.

28:40.280 --> 28:41.160
I'll wait for you for dinner.

28:41.160 --> 28:42.000
Okay.

28:46.200 --> 28:47.280
I got it, Grandma.

28:47.320 --> 28:48.050
I'm leaving.

29:10.480 --> 29:12.240
Since that happened,

29:12.800 --> 29:14.930
we haven't spoken a word to each other.

29:15.800 --> 29:17.680
We've never been like this

29:17.680 --> 29:18.800
before.

29:19.760 --> 29:21.290
The person I trusted so much

29:21.560 --> 29:23.090
lied to me for so many years.

29:23.520 --> 29:26.400
Every time I mocked his grades in the past,

29:27.320 --> 29:29.320
every time I tried hard to tutor him,

29:29.760 --> 29:32.090
and every time I worried about his future,

29:32.360 --> 29:33.800
looking back now,

29:34.240 --> 29:35.920
it all feels like a huge irony.

29:36.520 --> 29:37.840
And for the first time,

29:38.280 --> 29:39.960
I feel so distant from him.

29:40.600 --> 29:42.400
Across this short distance,

29:43.240 --> 29:46.120
it's like a galaxy between us.

29:55.200 --> 29:56.530
Yuanbao, what's wrong?

29:57.760 --> 29:58.520
I'm fine.

29:59.240 --> 30:00.500
Are you okay, Yuanbao?

30:01.080 --> 30:02.200
I'm fine, sir.

30:02.480 --> 30:04.320
Do you want to go to the infirmary?

30:04.320 --> 30:05.080
No need.

30:08.320 --> 30:09.320
Sorry, Mr. Xu.

30:09.480 --> 30:10.800
I need to talk to Yuanbao about something.

30:10.800 --> 30:11.800
Then you can go.

30:20.480 --> 30:23.440
Sir, what do you need me for?

30:23.880 --> 30:24.560
Yuanbao,

30:25.720 --> 30:27.180
your grandmother is sick.

30:27.440 --> 30:29.360
She just came out of the emergency room

30:29.360 --> 30:31.560
and was sent to the intensive care unit.

30:33.080 --> 30:33.800
Grandma.

30:33.800 --> 30:35.200
Yuanbao.

30:43.200 --> 30:45.040
Grandma was fine this morning.

30:46.200 --> 30:47.330
How did this happen?

30:47.880 --> 30:49.140
Why is this happening?

30:49.520 --> 30:51.960
The doctor said it's a heart problem.

30:53.480 --> 30:55.680
But we don't know the exact disease yet.

30:56.520 --> 30:59.360
We have to wait for the results to be sure.

31:04.960 --> 31:05.680
Auntie,

31:07.120 --> 31:09.720
is my grandma in danger?

31:11.640 --> 31:12.760
I don't know.

31:19.160 --> 31:19.840
Doctor,

31:20.520 --> 31:21.920
how are the test results?

31:24.320 --> 31:26.320
The aorta close to the human heart

31:26.360 --> 31:29.090
is called the thoracic aorta or ascending aorta.

31:29.280 --> 31:32.000
It consists of the intima, media, and adventitia.

31:32.000 --> 31:33.680
For various reasons,

31:33.800 --> 31:35.720
the vascular intima tears.

31:35.920 --> 31:37.840
Blood flows through the tear

31:37.960 --> 31:40.400
into the inner layer of the aorta,

31:40.520 --> 31:41.780
forming a false lumen.

31:41.920 --> 31:44.400
If blood continuously flows into this false lumen

31:44.400 --> 31:45.520
and cannot get out,

31:45.760 --> 31:48.400
it will keep tearing the blood vessel wall

31:48.600 --> 31:50.400
until the adventitia ruptures.

31:51.160 --> 31:51.960
Doctor,

31:52.720 --> 31:54.320
is it a very serious disease?

31:55.680 --> 31:58.000
It is quite a dangerous condition.

31:59.200 --> 32:01.330
Once the aortic dissection ruptures,

32:02.080 --> 32:04.640
the patient is prone to hemorrhagic shock,

32:04.920 --> 32:06.520
or even sudden death.

32:07.840 --> 32:09.800
If it ruptures into the thoracic cavity,

32:09.800 --> 32:12.280
hemothorax or hemoptysis will occur.

32:12.440 --> 32:14.040
In short, it's very serious.

32:14.160 --> 32:14.960
Doctor,

32:15.400 --> 32:16.560
if we do surgery,

32:17.360 --> 32:18.600
will she recover?

32:19.240 --> 32:20.240
Don't worry.

32:20.680 --> 32:21.320
We will

32:21.360 --> 32:23.640
develop the best treatment plan.

32:24.040 --> 32:25.970
But because the patient is too old,

32:26.240 --> 32:27.370
the top priority now

32:27.600 --> 32:28.960
is to control her blood pressure.

32:28.960 --> 32:30.200
We need to stabilize her condition.

32:30.200 --> 32:32.460
We absolutely cannot rush into surgery.

32:32.840 --> 32:35.770
I'm afraid she won't make it off the operating table.

32:35.960 --> 32:38.760
What are my grandmother's chances of survival?
